INSERT INTO public.organizations_agreements VALUES (1, 'vRisk Student Common Agreement', 'End User License Agreement
Cyber Innovative Technologies Security, Inc., Software License Terms
VRISK™
End User License Agreement


READ THIS IMPORTANT LEGAL NOTICE BEFORE PROCEEDING: This End User License Agreement (hereinafter Agreement), and the license terms set forth herein, constitute a binding legal agreement between Cyber Innovative Technologies Inc. (hereinafter CYBER INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES) and you, the End User (hereinafter End User). It is imperative that you carefully read this entire Agreement before you access or in any way use the CYBER INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES VRISK™ platform, website or access, download, install, copy or in any way use the VRISK™ Software, the website and the software which are the subject of this Agreement, because this Agreement governs your use of the website and software product made available to you by CYBER INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES and CYBER INTELLIGENCE 4U, Inc. in your course activities at Pace University.

