D. End User shall not, without the prior written consent of CYBER INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES or as otherwise provided by applicable law, in any way conduct, cause or permit the creation of any derivative works based on the VRISK Software or any element of the VRISK Software.

E. End User shall not, without the prior written consent of CYBER INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES or as otherwise provided by applicable law, in any way conduct, cause or permit the reverse engineering, disassembly, or decompiling, in whole or in part, of the VRISK Software; provided that, End User is hereby authorized to reverse engineer, disassemble or decompile only that portion of the VRISK Software which may be accessed and used by End User for the educational and training purposes for which the VRISK Software is offered by this license to the End User. End User may not reverse engineer, disassemble or decompile any part of the VRISK Software which is not available to End User for the sole purpose of education and training.

F. End User shall not, without the prior written consent of CYBER INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES or as otherwise provided by applicable law, in any way modify or alter, in whole or in part, the VRISK Software, the services and/or any documentation or material included with the VRISK Software; provided that, End User is hereby authorized to modify or alter only that portion of the VRISK Software which may be accessed and used by End User for the educational and training purposes for which the VRISK Software is offered by this license to the End User. End User may not modify or alter any part of the VRISK Software which is not available to End User for the sole purpose of education and training.

