I. Notwithstanding the terms and conditions of this Agreement, all or any portion of the VRISK Software which may constitute Third Party Software is licensed to End User subject to the terms and conditions of the software license agreement accompanying such Third-Party Software, in whatever form such license terms may be made available. Any and all use of such Third-Party Software by End User shall necessarily be governed solely and exclusively by the terms and conditions of such Third-Party license agreement.


III. PRICING AND RELATED MATTERS

A. When payment has been received by Cyber Intelligence 4U, Inc. for the Pace Enterprise Cybersecurity Program, CYBER INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES, End User will receive an email confirmation of the purchase which will include instructions for accessing the CYBER INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES VRISK Platform and the VRISK Software. Access will be granted when the End User accepts the terms set forth within this Agreement. Authorized End Users may only access the VRISK Software by way of the CYBER INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES VRisk Website, using credentials provided by CYBER INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES.

B. There shall be no refunds for failure to use the VRISK Software or any other reason, unless such reason is specifically set forth in this Agreement.


IV. OWNERSHIP OF SOFTWARE; SCOPE OF LICENSE; INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY

A. CYBER INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES does sell the VRisk Platform. For the Pace Program, CYBER INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES grants licenses for the use of its products. Therefore, this Agreement only gives the End User certain rights to use the VRISK Software described in this Agreement, and End User is limited in using this VRISK Software to the manner expressly set forth in this Agreement. All rights not specifically authorized to End Users in this Agreement are reserved by CYBER INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES.

B. The VRISK Software, as well as the structure, organization and code used by or in relation to the VRISK Software, and any and all corresponding documentation or information, is solely and exclusively owned by CYBER INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES. CYBER INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES owns all intellectual property rights, including applicable copyrights, patents and trademarks, which are in any way related to the VRISK Software and any and all corresponding documentation or information.

