XV. TERM AND TERMINATION; REMEDIES

A. This Agreement is effective upon receipt of payment by Cyber Intelligence 4U, Inc. for the Pace Enterprise Cybersecurity Program.  Cyber Intelligence 4U Inc. is the designee of CYBER INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES. CYBER INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES or its designee, or at such other time as may be established by the parties to this Agreement, and shall continue in effect for the period of time chosen by the End User, which shall be determined at the time of payment, based on pricing established by CYBER INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES.

B. Upon termination or expiration of this Agreement, End User shall immediately cease to use the VRISK Software and shall immediately destroy all copies or return them to CYBER INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES, unless this Agreement is renewed or extended, or a new Agreement is established by the parties.

C. Any unauthorized use of the VRISK Software by End User or any breach of this Agreement by End User shall result in the immediate and automatic termination of this Agreement, and shall also terminate any and all rights established for End User under this Agreement, without the need for further notice to End User by CYBER INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES. In the event of a termination of this Agreement based on this provision, CYBER INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES is authorized to block the use of the VRISK Software by End User, without any refund to End User. CYBER INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES reserves the right to seek criminal prosecution of End User and/or CYBER INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES reserves the right to bring a civil action against End User for any unauthorized use of the VRISK Software by End User or any breach of this Agreement by End User.

