E. In the event of a breach of this Agreement, End User agrees to pay CYBER INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES all reasonable costs and expenses incurred by CYBER INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES in the enforcement of this Agreement, including but not limited to, the reasonable fees of consultants, attorneys, courts costs and such other enforcement costs as may be incurred by CYBER INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES.

F. Any rights and obligations arising under the terms of this Agreement which are specifically identified herein as surviving termination of this Agreement, or which by their nature would be understood to remain in effect and survive the termination of this Agreement, shall remain in effect after termination of this Agreement.


XVI. TRANSFER OR ASSIGNMENT

Neither this Agreement as a whole, nor any part of this Agreement, nor any rights, duties or obligations arising hereunder, may be transferred or assigned directly or indirectly by End User without the prior written consent of CYBER INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES, which may be granted or denied at the sole discretion of CYBER INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES. Any such purported transfer or assignment without the prior written consent of CYBER INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES shall be null and void. This Agreement, and any related agreements, or rights, duties or obligations arising hereunder, may be transferred or assigned by CYBER INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES (a) pursuant to or in conjunction with a merger or change of control of CYBER INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES or (b) to an assignee of all or substantially all of the outstanding shares of CYBER INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES.


XVII. APPLICABLE LAW; JURISDICTIONAL MATTERS

