XVIII. NOTICE

All notices under this Agreement to be sent to CYBER INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES shall be sent by U.S. Postal Service certified mail, to either: (1) the CYBER INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES mailing address set forth on CYBER INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES’S website, Cyberinnovativetech.com, or (2) 555 Madison Ave. 5th Floor, New York, NY 10022. All notices under this Agreement to be sent by CYBER INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES to End Users shall be sent (1) by any available electronic means; or (2) by any other means as may be determined by CYBER INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES, in its sole discretion, to be appropriate.


XIX. EFFECT OF WAIVER OF RIGHT

